THE VIDEO WAS A STORY ABOUT A BOY WHO THOUGHT HE WAS RICH, UNTIL HIS FATHER OPENLY EXPLAINED TO HIM THAT THEY WERE, IN FACT POOR.
THE FATHER THEN BECAME EMPLOYED AS A JANITOR AT A LIBRARY.
THIS MEANT THAT THE BOY AND HIS FAMILY WOULD LIVE ABOVE THE LIBRARY.
BECAUSE OF THIS, THE BOY HAD ACCESS TO THE LIBRARY WHENEVER HE PLEASE, EVEN AFTER THE LIBRARY HAD CLOSED.
THIS CAUSED KIDS TO POINT OUT THAT HE LITERALLY LIVED IN THE LIBRARY.
HOWEVER, THE BOY FOUND COMFORT IN READING BOOKS AND THIS KNEW WEALTH OF KNOWLEDGE WOULD EVENTUALLY INSPIRE HIM TO PURSUE A HIGHER EDUCATION.
SOMETHING THAT HAD NEVER OCCURRED IN HIS FAMILY PREVIOUS TO HIM.
THE BOY EVENTUALLY WENT ON TO BECOME A PROFESSOR AND EVEN INVITED HIS FATHER TO TAKE A LOOK AT THE PLAQUE ON HIS WALL AT HIS JOB.
HIS WAS FATHER WAS SILENT, BUT PROUD.
